{"tid":44573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唯物論/唯心論]究竟點樣證明自己既記憶係真?","createTime":"2016-12-18T11:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T22:02:32.000Z","uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c12362c7bf19458b7e5557895896ba65510928","tid":44573,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"特別係好細好細個既記憶<br />\n我好記得我6，7歲時砌左好多模型<br />\n但俾我細佬掉哂落街，我細佬當時一兩歲<br />\n<br />\n近排講返件事<br />\n但我細佬依家就反駁話<br />\n一個一兩歲既細路冇可能行埋窗邊再掉哂啲野落街一件不留<br />\n佢話我既記憶係假既<br />\n仲話我當時得6，7歲，更加冇財力去買咁多模型<br />\n懷疑我根本冇擁有過，一切都係我太想擁有而喺自己腦海虛構出黎<br />\n因為朝思暮想，逐漸成為左記憶既一部分<br />\n<br />\n冇人證，冇物證<br />\n點樣可以知道呢段記憶係真定假<br />\n我真係有段好深刻既記憶係我辛辛苦苦砌好哂既模型<br />\n俾我細佬掉哂落街"},{"pid":"d511dfc2ba9ed5b823dfe091bd1455205fe99d4c","tid":44573,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c396e990ff55cf7fb0d93157ea95d807e621999","tid":44573,"uid":19406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曼徳拉效應"},{"pid":"f3ad5bd3d4b831c5c47bc7ebc5b7aa0bb9b2ae80","tid":44573,"uid":9358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"人既記憶好信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n可以聽下呢條ted talk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHow reliable is your memory?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ted.com/talks/elizabeth_loftus_the_fiction_of_memory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ted.com%2Ftalks%2Felizabeth_loftus_the_fiction_of_memory&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=6fa35ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ted.com/talks/elizabeth_loftus_the_fiction_of_memory</a>"},{"pid":"a7e9a7d9a7cfa82daa436219270dba872f997530","tid":44573,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74324c4d3d9d221d865dfa69e3aaa94dc581844e","tid":44573,"uid":4297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:59:47.000Z","msg":"其實無<br />\n好似鋼鍊個艾力克斯無咗肉身太耐<br />\n已經唔肯定自己係咪真係人咁解"},{"pid":"a86ad04bf1f17d76a5acee413bedf9db1b244fbe","tid":44573,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/L88mBul.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FL88mBul.jpg&h=8b486782&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0116057d5bfeb889f7f687ee2ee60adcf70f7db4","tid":44573,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:02:59.000Z","msg":"其實無<br />\n可能你今日訓醒 你腦入面琴日到之前既記憶都係岩岩植入<br />\n你只係岩岩新做既驅彀"},{"pid":"777d8ba568f45690c9fccc0a5f2b36fe8feeaf92","tid":44573,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"我撐你細佬呀<br />\n我都比人屈過我部psp係黑色<br />\n借左比佢玩成粒鐘<br />\n明明就係藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980c4d5550d966dc42925d9323904dfee0b9639c","tid":44573,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:28:25.000Z","msg":"明明成件事就係你玩玩下黎手掉左落街<br />\n但係你又怕你老母發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚佢屌鳩你<br />\n所以你就走去同你老母講<br />\n屈你細佬話係佢掉落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468e9560beebdcd53be38a238bd369b105f182f5","tid":44573,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明成件事就係你玩玩下黎手掉左落街<br />\n但係你又怕你老母發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚佢屌鳩你<br />\n所以你就走去同你老母講<br />\n屈你細佬話係佢掉落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔知點解我好深刻既記憶係我細佬丟<br />\n但依家死無對證<br />\n我都唔知係我自己幻想定係真有其事"},{"pid":"3332a8a26f4714e4e5569b85d12a58609b18b9b9","tid":44573,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"You don't. <br />\n當故事睇, news story 同 歷史故事可以真可以假"},{"pid":"45bb4e7806bd51d0e0603e735585645c2753a2a5","tid":44573,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"唔放學術台？"},{"pid":"9cd61cdcd9015bb343d2713825fe7c1b27c22334","tid":44573,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔放學術台？</blockquote><br />\n唔知放咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩admin移post"},{"pid":"335bf1f22d584554e02c61b0f873bcbf040df540","tid":44573,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"人嘅記憶係好唔可信，我記得有實驗show到人係會虛構記憶去填補空白"},{"pid":"a717c22335673ad3db3d794d149005fe1c741903","tid":44573,"uid":67056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人嘅記憶係好唔可信，我記得有實驗show到人係會虛構記憶去填補空白</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都聽過 同埋記憶越遠會越模糊"},{"pid":"d1a7004835cc214d65fadfe5dd99ed2350bddf09","tid":44573,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人嘅記憶係好唔可信，我記得有實驗show到人係會虛構記憶去填補空白</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都聽過 同埋記憶越遠會越模糊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但間唔中會報道有D過目不忘既奇人🤔"},{"pid":"0edf141a706820680e8a74ba272ee98f49d69a18","tid":44573,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"你可以試下落街問下人十幾年前有冇試過有一日有好多模型飛落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b7e4eb697158d4b3fbbe0498873ea05e042667","tid":44573,"uid":33623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"Last thursdayism <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2e4c48c340561244792f512e0ff4b45bb70d40","tid":44573,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"我記得細個係七樓跳左落黎"},{"pid":"98a2331e927a2ae98bdcc27439a3c32ea277d3e3","tid":44573,"uid":9930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:01:25.000Z","msg":"係咪睇完鋼鍊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977a3486b17122c68ba3ce3ba25d28f7734da8e5","tid":44573,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T21:45:03.000Z","msg":"通常D仆街, 屈開人果D記性得別好<br />\n記性差果D都係比人屈果D<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為係因為係記性差先比人屈<br />\n其實係比人屈到記性差<br />\n<br />\n屈開人果D因為知道自己咁仆街, 人地都一樣可以咁仆街<br />\n所以比人屈果陣都會好確信自己記憶冇錯, 因為佢知道大把人好似佢自己咁會屈鳩人<br />\n但比人屈開果D, 就唔太相信真係有好多仆街大事小事都屈鳩人, 所以佢地會懷疑係自己記錯, 久而久之就真係變記性差"},{"pid":"dd7361c0199d2ef81f8cdbd14fdef654f90e0044","tid":44573,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T22:02:32.000Z","msg":"其實你只係一個host<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}